{"id":429080,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/02/台湾台南地震第8天-死亡人数超过百人/","date":"2016-02-13T07:04:09Z","modified":"2016-02-13T07:05:35Z","title":"BBC｜台湾台南地震第8天 死亡人数超过百人","content":"<div id=\"attachment_429082\" style=\"width: 585px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213031033_a_member_of_rescue_teams_stands_by_as_heavy_excavation_machinery_continues_to_dig_through_the_rubble_of_a_collapsed_building_complex_in_tainan_taiwan_976x549_ap_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-429082\"><img class=\"wp-image-429082\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213031033_a_member_of_rescue_teams_stands_by_as_heavy_excavation_machinery_continues_to_dig_through_the_rubble_of_a_collapsed_building_complex_in_tainan_taiwan_976x549_ap_nocredit.jpg\" alt=\"160213031033_a_member_of_rescue_teams_stands_by_as_heavy_excavation_machinery_continues_to_dig_through_the_rubble_of_a_collapsed_building_complex_in_tainan_taiwan_976x549_ap_nocredit\" width=\"575\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213031033_a_member_of_rescue_teams_stands_by_as_heavy_excavation_machinery_continues_to_dig_through_the_rubble_of_a_collapsed_building_complex_in_tainan_taiwan_976x549_ap_nocredit.jpg 660w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213031033_a_member_of_rescue_teams_stands_by_as_heavy_excavation_machinery_continues_to_dig_through_the_rubble_of_a_collapsed_building_complex_in_tainan_taiwan_976x549_ap_nocredit-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">一名救援人员站在倒塌的维冠金龙大楼废墟上。维冠金龙大楼的倒塌导致重大伤亡，开发商已接受司法调查。</p></div>\n<p>台湾台南地震8天后，台南市政府统计称，截至周六（2月13日）早上八点，永康区维冠金龙大楼已经106死，待救9人。加上归仁区2名罹难者，地震死亡人数累计108人。</p>\n<p>台湾中央社稍后引用台南市政府统计称，截至今天上午11時，地震共造成台南市112死，其中永康维冠大楼死亡110死，待救5人。 周五晚间的官方统计称地震造成97人死27人失踪。随着时间推移，最近两天在现场发现的死亡人数迅速增加。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_429081\" style=\"width: 585px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213030510__monk_and_visitors_facing_on_the_photos_of_earthquake_victims_pray_during_a_memorial_service_in_tainan_taipei_12_february_2016_976x549_epa_nocredit.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-429081\"><img class=\"wp-image-429081\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213030510__monk_and_visitors_facing_on_the_photos_of_earthquake_victims_pray_during_a_memorial_service_in_tainan_taipei_12_february_2016_976x549_epa_nocredit.jpg\" alt=\"12日，台南地震家属在追思灵堂。 \" width=\"575\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213030510__monk_and_visitors_facing_on_the_photos_of_earthquake_victims_pray_during_a_memorial_service_in_tainan_taipei_12_february_2016_976x549_epa_nocredit.jpg 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/02/160213030510__monk_and_visitors_facing_on_the_photos_of_earthquake_victims_pray_during_a_memorial_service_in_tainan_taipei_12_february_2016_976x549_epa_nocredit-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">12日，台南地震家属在追思灵堂。</p></div>\n<p>台湾中央社报道称，维冠大楼已有106死，待救人数是8大人、1小孩，分别是A栋1大人，B栋1大人，G栋6大人、1小孩。台南市长赖清德当天指示，必须挖到地底下2至3公尺，直到没有建筑本体为主，才能确信全部找遍。</p>\n<p>此前一天，台南地检署已提讯在押的维冠建商林明辉，并由检察事务官带同林明辉到位于永大五路的住处搜索，同时传唤相关证人到庭厘清案情。</p>\n<p>台南地震造成维冠大楼倒塌，造成严重伤亡，迄今为止绝大多数死亡人员来自维冠大楼。</p>\n<p>台湾总统马英九已表示，这起倒塌事故不是天灾而是“人祸”。当初的房屋如果能盖牢固，就能避免遗憾。</p>\n","author":999,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,8779],"tags":[30199,10599,30261,9820]}